<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Imgur Gallery</title><link>https://imgur.com</link><description>description</description><lastBuildDate>2025-01-24 16:16:02.709819</lastBuildDate><item><title>Image says it all</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/1Tg32xa</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UfCNnmV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I used Imgur when I was deployed as well. It helps to laugh at shit posts. Even in 2009 Imgur was awesome. 

I come back to shitpost once in a while when I’m having a hard time. I had a feeling today I haven’t had in a while. I felt like I was about to be hit by something. 

